# P2.1 — Multi-Language Agent Templates
**Phase**: p2.1 | **Semantic**: v0.4.0 | **Status**: ✅ COMPLETE

Historical note: implemented and merged via PR #8. Keep this file as delivered-plan documentation.

---

## Overview

**Goal**: Agents generati con awareness linguistico. Risposte in IT/EN/ES/FR con vincoli styleguide culturali.

**Example workflow**:
```
User project: "FastAPI backend + PostgreSQL"
Project language setting: "it_IT"
    ↓
rgen generates agents
    ↓
esperto_backend.md → Italian style guide + Italian examples
esperto_database.md → Italian terminology + Italian best practices
    ↓
Agent responses adopt tone/language of project
```

**Acceptance**:
- Support 4 lingue minimo (IT, EN, ES, FR)
- Fallback a EN se lingua manca
- i18n structure nel knowledge_base
- CLI flag `--language it|en|es|fr` (default: detect from metadata)
- Test coverage > 85%

---

