**Example test**:
```python
def test_end_to_end_italian_generation(tmp_path):
    """Test full Italian agent generation."""
    detector = LanguageDetector()
    lang = detector.detect_from_metadata({"language": "it"})

    assert lang == "it"

    localizer = TemplateLocalizer(lang)
    template = localizer.load_template("psm_stack", "backend")

    assert "Esperto Backend" in template
    assert "{{LANGUAGE}}" not in template  # Should be substituted
```

